---
title: Cajun-Spiced Jumbo Shrimp Bowl with Avocado and Sriracha Mayo
description: Our juicy shrimp is the star of the show here. It's drizzled with an umami-packed sriracha mayo and served over a vibrant salad packed with creamy avocado and plump tomatoes.
